'''Permaglass''' was a transparent substance used in the making of windows. The windows of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine's]] apartment at [[500 Republica/Legends|500 Republica]] were made of it, as were the windows at the [[LiMerge Building/Legends|LiMerge building]] in [[The Works/Legends|The Works]], where Palpatine met with [[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku]] prior to and during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

